{"_id":"yzlt16fqedi","name":"Accurate Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an accurate attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on the effect modifier of the attack and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"qes93hzyjz","name":"Agile Feint","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use your Acrobatics bonus or movement speed rank in place of Deception to feint and trick in combat.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"xlaj6ybpwzq","name":"All-out Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an all-out attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on your active defenses (Dodge and Parry) and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"vechrnwqkko","name":"Improved Initiative","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+4 bonus to initiative checks per rank.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"ofgpuymur3g","name":"Iron Will","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+2 circumstance bonus on Will resistance checks.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"9cas7sn83dj","name":"Great Endurance","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+5 bonus on checks to avoid fatigue and to hold your breath.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"zzq20bgvre","name":"Evasion","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+2 circumstance bonus to Dodge checks to avoid area effects. Rank 2 increases bonus to +5.</p>","rang":2}}
{"_id":"ied28s8yld","name":"Attractive","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+2 circumstance bonus on Deception and Persuasion checks (+5 for rank 2).</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"diyq1693gi","name":"Eidetic Memory","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Perfect recall. +5 circumstance bonus on memory checks. Can make Expertise checks as if trained.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"vxm7mnm5pum","name":"Animal Empathy","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have a special connection with animals. You can use interaction skills on animals normally.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"9qxoizqd2yg","name":"Artificer","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use the Expertise: Magic skill to create temporary magical devices.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"xgm8a6g6gja","name":"Assessment","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use Insight to able to judge an opponent’s relative combat capabilities.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"xfc8evkyee","name":"Beginner's Luck","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>By spending a hero point, you gain an effective 5 ranks in a skill in which you currently have 0 ranks.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"mzz46gaal6h","name":"Benefit","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have some significant social or structural benefit, such as wealth, status, or a secret identity.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"k52utijahfd","name":"Chokehold","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>If you successfully grab and maintain a hold on an opponent, you can suffocate them.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"0e0pbug5drk","name":"Connected","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You know people who can help you out. You can call in favors by making a Persuasion check.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"rg72c3k5z5m","name":"Contacts","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have extensive contacts. You can make an Investigation check to gather information in only one minute.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"5wpf3pbz27f","name":"Daze","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can make a Deception or Intimidation check as a standard action to cause an opponent to hesitate in combat.</p>","rang":2}}
{"_id":"r187fddtmek","name":"Defensive Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Trade up to -5 attack bonus for an equal bonus (+5) to active defenses.</p>","rang":1}}
